title: Where can i find something like this India?
selftext: Hi folks, Can someone suggest where can i find key chain like this in India.
comments: Is it reliable i never tried.
I’m not sure if they would ship to India but you can check out the Esty App and ask the seller if they will ship to you
Yes, I have gotten really cute and handmade items from Florida and Uk. But you’ll have to pay the shipping charges.

I ordered a handmade dream catcher, slightly on the expensive side but worth every penny. I have searched on many websites here in India, but nothing as full and heavy and good looking for the size that I wanted.

If you are ordering a small keychain, then it might become unnecessarily expensive.
Yes i am getting this for 1.3 K ig.what is the delivery time

It’ll usually be put on the website. The personalised wooden board took like 5 days to reach from US after ordering. But the personalised dream catcher took a month and a few days. 

So they usually put on the website as to how many days for international orders.
